Package com.foreach.across.modules.graphql.entity.schema

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GraphQLEntityTypeConfiguration
    Represents the type configuration rules for a type based on an entity configuration.
    GraphQLSchemaFactory
    Responsible for building the GraphQLSchema by building all the provided EntityGraphQLListQueryConfiguration into queries, types and dataFetchers.
    GraphQLSchemaRegistrar
    Base class for any implementation that wishes to extend a schema being generated.
    GraphQLTypeDescriptionResolver
    Resolver to get the GraphQL descriptions from the message source.
    GraphQLTypeRegistry
    Can be used to resolve the GraphQL type for a Java type.
    JavaScalars
    Provides Registry to resolve GraphQL Query Java Scalar Types Converts java types into base GraphQLType
